ZH: 每个星期一我去游泳。
EN: I go swimming every Monday.

ZH: 每天早上我都喝咖啡。
EN: I drink coffee every morning.

ZH: 每个学生必须完成作业。
EN: Every student must complete their homework.

ZH: 每年的春节都很热闹。
EN: The Spring Festival is lively every year.

ZH: 每辆火车都会停在这个站台。
EN: Every train will stop at this platform.

ZH: 每家餐馆都有特色菜。
EN: Every restaurant has its own specialty dish.

ZH: 每个孩子都应该受到尊重。
EN: Every child should be respected.

ZH: 每次我去图书馆都会借很多书。
EN: I borrow a lot of books every time I go to the library.

ZH: 每个项目都需要团队合作。
EN: Teamwork is required for every project.

ZH: 每次见到你我都很高兴。
EN: I am always happy to see you every time.

ZH: 每一个问题都有解决的方法。
EN: There is a solution to every problem.

ZH: 每天多喝水对健康很重要。
EN: Drinking plenty of water every day is important for health.

ZH: 每场比赛都有胜者和失败者。
EN: There is a winner and a loser in every game.

ZH: 每一条街道都有不同的商店。
EN: Each street has different shops.

ZH: 每个工作日我都坐地铁上班。
EN: I take the subway to work every weekday.

ZH: 每个人都有自己的优点和缺点。
EN: Everyone has their own strengths and weaknesses.

ZH: 每次我去购物都会花很多钱。
EN: I spend a lot of money every time I go shopping.

ZH: 每个城市都有自己的特色和文化。
EN: Every city has its own unique characteristics and culture.

ZH: 每逢周末我都会去郊外散步。
EN: I go for a walk in the countryside every weekend.

ZH: 每一次我听到这首歌都会感到很开心。
EN: I feel happy every time I hear this song.
